          <tr><td>Convection fan motor</td><td>$380–$620</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Steam generator heating element</td><td>$420–$680</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Control board (SCC or iCombi Pro)</td><td>$850–$1,500</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="small">Most Rational calls land $400–$850 parts-and-labor; steam generator and control board jobs run at the higher end. See our <a href="/price-list/commercial-oven-repair-cost/">commercial oven repair cost guide</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Related Rational and commercial oven peer pages</h2>
      <ul class="related-links">
