        <li><a href="/commercial/oven-repair/">All commercial oven repair in Los Angeles →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/price-list/commercial-oven-repair-cost/">Commercial oven repair cost guide →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/west-hollywood/">West Hollywood service area</a> · <a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena service area</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Rational combi oven repair — frequently asked</h2>
      {faqs.map(f => (
        <details class="faq">
          <summary>{f.q}</summary>
          <p set:html={f.a}></p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Rational combi down? Call the branch nearest your kitchen.</h2>
      <p>Same-day in LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. $120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair.</p>
      <div class="branches">
        <a href="tel:+13238704790"><b>West Hollywood</b><span>(323) 870-4790</span></a>
        <a href="tel:+14243250520"><b>Los Angeles</b><span>(424) 325-0520</span></a>
        <a href="tel:+14242080228"><b>Thousand Oaks</b><span>(424) 208-0228</span></a>
        <a href="tel:+16263764458"><b>Pasadena</b><span>(626) 376-4458</span></a>
        <a href="tel:+12134019019"><b>Irvine</b><span>(213) 401-9019</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="float-call" aria-label="Call now">☎ Call (424) 325-0520</a>
</Layout>

